lines.text: I'm married to the Frigid Witch of the West.
All you talk about is growing old together. I'm not ready to grow old!
I want the LUST to be there.
If you love somebody, you do what's natural, and that's enough.
[Fran doesn't want to have sex at all]
I feel like I'm being punished.
I am so sick and tired of being the other woman.
Getting a divorce is the only way we can stay friends.
